title: FC Cincinnati shows off new jerseys
text:
FC Cincinnati shows off new jerseys Season to kick off April 2016 UPDATED 11:24 PM EDT Oct 07, 2015 More 
FC Cincinnati's head coach, John Harkes, and the owners revealed the team sponsor is Toyota. 
The team had an open house for fans at Nippert Stadium where the team will play next year. 
Harkes said he's already looking in Cincinnati for players. 
"Today I was at St. X watching a training session, seen UC game twice and catching them online as well on ESPN 3, so we're pretty familiar with what we're looking at here and there may be some great opportunities for players that are local," Harkes said. 
The FC Cincinnati season kicks off in April 2016.
